    "en": {
      "title": "Covid for Dhananjaya and Vandersay",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dhananjaya de Silva and Geoffrey Vandersay, two players of the Sri Lankan team who were scheduled to participate in the Test match against Australia, have been infected with the Covid virus.",
        "Instead of those two players, Prabhat Jayasuriya and Lakshan Sandakan have been called to the squad.",
        "Earlier, Angelo Mathews and Praveen Jayawickrama were also infected with the Covid virus."
      ],
